{
  "stem": "2578.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But since he was a doctor-- what he did, being a doctor, I don't know, because there was no way for him to do anything for us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First of all, as far as-- as far as being sick, everybody was sick.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As far as being not capable to work, no one was able to do anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But his job was primarily to decide who--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's why.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I was laying-- oh, this happened a little later, when, the-- I was laying with people on my-- on my bunk.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because these-- we had bunks, there were about 10, 12 people laying on those-- on those bunks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I would sit-- I would lay on these-- on this bunk with others, and we were talking to each other.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And suddenly somebody would be quiet, and then we realized that-- that he-- he died.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we just didn't pay attention to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We let them-- we let them-- we would let them lay there until a certain kommando among the inmates would come in and take him down and take him outside to-- to be dropped into some sort of a grave.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not a grave, but a ditch, to be filled up with-- with some sort of a chemical and covered with dirt.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never found him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was told by a friend of ours, from our hometown, who knew us well, that he was with my brother in a camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was among the young group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they did very light, or very easy work, for a short amount of time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the whole group was shipped out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't know, at the time, that he was shipped to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
